kalau aku punya motif lain.

725
00:52:38.780 --> 00:52:41.790
Benar.

726
00:52:41.790 --> 00:52:45.320
Akupun mencintaimu, Suk Hun.

727
00:52:45.320 --> 00:52:47.910
